00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:34.410
It is said to be an island six days north of Britain, where in

00:00:34.410 --> 00:00:38.860
the summer there is no night and in the winter there is no light.

00:00:39.210 --> 00:00:46.230
To this day, there is no agreement on exactly where Thule is, but there are plenty of theories.

00:00:46.510 --> 00:00:53.800
So, in this episode we are going to explore the mystery of Thule, where the story of its

